prompts.frontCover: Humorous greeting card front cover, beautiful watercolor painting style with soft, blended colors. The scene is a ridiculously cute and exaggerated beach paradise. A cartoon/illustrated version of Lao Lao from the reference photo is gleefully floating on her back in the calm, turquoise ocean water, wearing sunglasses and a bright floral swimsuit, with a huge, happy smile. She is holding an oversized, giant boba milk tea cup on her stomach with both hands, sipping from a ridiculously long straw. A cartoon/illustrated version of Jordan from the reference photo is standing knee-deep in the water next to her, playfully sprinkling giant tapioca pearls (the size of beach balls) from a bucket onto her, like confetti. The sky is a dreamy pastel watercolor wash of pink and orange. In the background, palm trees have boba cups hanging from them like coconuts. Centered in the middle of the design, in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday to my bestea, Lao Lao!". Flat 2D artwork for printing, vibrant and joyful colors.
